2","tid":1642870,"uid":156914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T01:36:48.000Z","msg":"蒙面法後大家義憤填膺咁十八區裝修活動，但裝修活動已經遇到瓶頸位，我地係裝修程度同選擇都出現分歧，呢刻我認為應該用文宣開花黎承接裝修活動。<br />\n<br />\n文宣我地不嬲有做，但可唔可以黎次大規模嘅十八區文宣開花，文宣形式不限，傳單、memo、寫字、噴漆不拘；地點隨心，但最好係紅藍店、當眼處、當區連儂、各處隧道天橋要道。咁做係為左三點<br />\n<br />\n1.解釋之前裝修活動嘅原因<br />\n2.承接整個運動嘅流動，免於因靜態而消退<br />\n3.推廣接落黎嘅行動，同加強全民口罩嘅傳播率<br />\n<br />\n文武兼備先係我地贏嘅重點，每一條線我地都唔可以放棄，唔好再戇鳩鳩坐係到等外國打救，我地如果乜都唔做，神仙都救我地唔到<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n願榮光歸香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:18:32.000Z","msg":"印緊, 今晚自己個區通街貼!!!"},{"pid":"2dddf5bf67691865edb2f87985e6969a56b12c76","tid":1642870,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:19:46.000Z","msg":"敵人唔提既我地要繼續做 幫支那系列銀行裝修 燒支共黨旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40721ed24bbf16d71025c205d878aa7b3343e0ed","tid":1642870,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:20:28.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"31330363acc81b22a01d9523de3b24b43b99fd5f","tid":1642870,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:21:12.000Z","msg":"仲有咁撚多中資你話咩話？"},{"pid":"1ba64da66fb0ee0c9354d51d0c9be148bb69c15f","tid":1642870,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:22:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec84c604b45b5992b168bfba19a8b43189af0540","tid":1642870,"uid":257755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:23:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OUQA8WF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOUQA8WF.jpg&h=64cb86e8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CD2LMJr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCD2LMJr.jpg&h=ff9f2d18&s={SIZE}\" /> 外